rComments: He doesn't explain concepts clearly at all, or give proper examples for the homework.  I found myself needing an inordinate amount of outside help and even then I still had a very difficult time with the class.
Avoid takin him, take the alternate section for this course.

Definitely one of the easiest math professors.  His exams come straight from the book and rarely do they need to be curved.  They homework load tends to be light too.  He's also taught Math 415 and Math 385 so try to take those classes with him if you can.
